#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:155
msgid ""
"It depends only on `perry-ffi` and `serde_json`. Zero references to `perry-"
"runtime` internals. That's the bar for every wrapper that moves out of "
"`perry-stdlib` over the course of #466 Phase 5."
