#: src/ui/overview.md:29 src/tui/overview.md:44
msgid "Mental Model"
msgstr "Modelo Mental"

#: src/ui/overview.md:31
msgid ""
"Perry's UI follows the same model as SwiftUI and Flutter: you compose native"
" widgets using stack-based layout containers (`VStack`, `HStack`, `ZStack`),"
" control alignment and distribution, and style widgets via free functions "
"that take the widget handle as their first argument (`textSetColor(label, r,"
" g, b, a)`, `widgetSetEdgeInsets(stack, ...)`, etc.). If you're coming from "
"web development, the key shift is:"
msgstr ""
"La UI de Perry sigue el mismo modelo que SwiftUI y Flutter: compones widgets"
" nativos usando contenedores de layout basados en stacks (`VStack`, "
"`HStack`, `ZStack`), controlas la alineación y distribución, y aplicas "
"estilos a los widgets mediante funciones libres que toman el handle del "
"widget como primer argumento (`textSetColor(label, r, g, b, a)`, "
"`widgetSetEdgeInsets(stack, ...)`, etc.). Si vienes del desarrollo web, el "
"cambio clave es:"

#: src/ui/overview.md:33
msgid ""
"**Layout** is controlled by stack alignment, distribution, and spacers — not"
" CSS properties. See [Layout](layout.md)."
msgstr ""
"El **Layout** se controla mediante la alineación, distribución y "
"espaciadores del stack — no con propiedades CSS. Consulta "
"[Layout](layout.md)."

#: src/ui/overview.md:34
msgid ""
"**Styling** is applied directly to widgets — not through stylesheets. See "
"[Styling](styling.md)."
msgstr ""
"El **Estilado** se aplica directamente a los widgets — no a través de hojas "
"de estilo. Consulta [Estilado](styling.md)."

#: src/ui/overview.md:35
msgid ""
"**Absolute positioning** uses overlays (`widgetAddOverlay` + "
"`widgetSetOverlayFrame`) — not `position: absolute/relative`."
msgstr ""
"El **posicionamiento absoluto** usa overlays (`widgetAddOverlay` + "
"`widgetSetOverlayFrame`) — no `position: absolute/relative`."

#: src/ui/overview.md:36
msgid ""
"**Design tokens** come from the `perry-styling` package. See "
"[Theming](theming.md)."
msgstr ""
"Los **design tokens** provienen del paquete `perry-styling`. Consulta "
"[Temas](theming.md)."

