"Icon appears in the notification area (bottom-right). Left-click → `onClick`"
" callback. Right-click → menu. PNG and `.ico` paths supported (PNG via "
"`LoadImageW` with `LR_LOADFROMFILE`). `trayCreate` must come after "
"`App({...})` since the tray reuses the main window's `WndProc`."
msgstr ""
"El ícono aparece en el área de notificaciones (inferior derecha). Clic "
"izquierdo → callback `onClick`. Clic derecho → menú. Se admiten rutas PNG y "
"`.ico` (PNG mediante `LoadImageW` con `LR_LOADFROMFILE`). `trayCreate` debe "
"ejecutarse después de `App({...})` ya que la bandeja reutiliza el `WndProc` "
"de la ventana principal."

