"`perry.splash` config in `package.json`. The splash screen appears instantly"
" during cold start."
msgstr ""
"Perry genera automáticamente un `LaunchScreen.storyboard` nativo a partir de"
" la configuración `perry.splash` en `package.json`. La pantalla de inicio "
"aparece de inmediato durante el arranque en frío."

#: src/platforms/ios.md:107
msgid ""
"The image is centered at 128x128pt with `scaleAspectFit`. You can provide a "
