msgstr "Paquetes Compatibles"

#: src/stdlib/overview.md:22
msgid "Networking & HTTP"
msgstr "Redes y HTTP"

#: src/stdlib/overview.md:23
msgid ""
"**node:http** / **node:https** / **node:http2** — Node.js stdlib HTTP server"
" modules + WebSocket upgrade dispatch (issue #577). The full "
"`IncomingMessage` / `ServerResponse` surface plus TLS via rustls and HTTP/2 "
"via ALPN. See [HTTP & Networking](http.md#nodejs-compatibility--nodehttp--"
"nodehttps--nodehttp2)."
msgstr ""
"**node:http** / **node:https** / **node:http2** — Módulos de servidor HTTP "
"de la stdlib de Node.js + despacho de actualización WebSocket (issue #577). "
"La superficie completa de `IncomingMessage` / `ServerResponse` más TLS vía "
"rustls y HTTP/2 vía ALPN. Ver [HTTP y Redes](http.md#nodejs-compatibility--"
"nodehttp--nodehttps--nodehttp2)."

#: src/stdlib/overview.md:24
msgid ""
"**hono** — runtime-agnostic web framework. `app.fetch` works end-to-end via "
"`compilePackages` (testing + edge runtimes). Long-lived port-listening "
"server pattern is currently blocked on "
"[\\#589](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/589). See [HTTP & "
"Networking → Hono](http.md#hono)."
msgstr ""
"**hono** — framework web independiente del runtime. `app.fetch` funciona de "
"extremo a extremo vía `compilePackages` (testing + runtimes edge). El patrón"
" de servidor con escucha persistente está actualmente bloqueado en "
"[\\#589](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/589). Ver [HTTP y Redes → "
"Hono](http.md#hono)."

