#: src/stdlib/http.md:385
msgid ""
"The full SigV4 signing chain (Web Crypto HMAC-SHA-256 + SHA-256, "
"TextEncoder, URLSearchParams, Headers iteration, typed-array byte "
"marshalling) is exercised end-to-end. Read paths (`getObject`, `statObject`,"
" `deleteObject`, `listObjects`, `presignedGetObject`, `presignedPostObject`)"
" are verified byte-identical to `bun` against pinned test vectors and will "
"authenticate against real S3."
msgstr ""
"La cadena completa de firma SigV4 (Web Crypto HMAC-SHA-256 + SHA-256, "
"TextEncoder, URLSearchParams, iteración de Headers, marshalling de bytes con"
" typed arrays) se ejecuta de extremo a extremo. Las rutas de lectura "
"(`getObject`, `statObject`, `deleteObject`, `listObjects`, "
"`presignedGetObject`, `presignedPostObject`) se verifican byte a byte contra"
" `bun` con vectores de prueba fijados y autenticarán correctamente contra S3"
" real."

#: src/stdlib/http.md:387
msgid ""
"Multipart uploads (`putObject` with a `ReadableStream` source large enough "
"to chunk) exercise additional surface — `WritableStream` / `TransformStream`"
" subclassing per #562 — that path compiles but isn't independently verified "
"against pinned vectors here."
msgstr ""
"Las subidas multiparte (`putObject` con una fuente `ReadableStream` "
"suficientemente grande para fragmentarse) ejercitan superficie adicional — "
"subclases de `WritableStream` / `TransformStream` según #562 — esa ruta "
"compila pero no está verificada de forma independiente contra vectores "
"fijados aquí."

#: src/stdlib/http.md:389
msgid ""
"For the AWS SDK v3 (`@aws-sdk/client-s3`): Perry currently can't compile it."
" Its dependency tree pulls in `@smithy/*` and runtime middleware "
"registration that uses `Proxy` and dynamic property assignment, neither of "
"which is in Perry's [TypeScript subset](../language/limitations.md). "
"`@bradenmacdonald/s3-lite-client` covers the same surface "
"(Put/Get/Head/Delete/List/presign + multipart) for almost every real-world "
"need."
msgstr ""
"Para el AWS SDK v3 (`@aws-sdk/client-s3`): Perry actualmente no puede "
"compilarlo. Su árbol de dependencias incluye `@smithy/*` y registro de "
"middleware en tiempo de ejecución que utiliza `Proxy` y asignación dinámica "
"de propiedades, ninguno de los cuales está en el [subconjunto de "
"TypeScript](../language/limitations.md) de Perry. `@bradenmacdonald/s3-lite-"
"client` cubre la misma superficie (Put/Get/Head/Delete/List/presign + "
"multiparte) para casi cualquier necesidad del mundo real."

