msgstr "`isolated()`"

#: src/container/security.md:179 src/container/security.md:180
#: src/container/security.md:181
msgid "✅"
msgstr "✅"

#: src/container/security.md:180
msgid "`hardened()`"
msgstr "`hardened()`"

#: src/container/security.md:181
msgid "`untrusted()`"
msgstr "`untrusted()`"

#: src/container/security.md:181
msgid "**required**"
msgstr "**obligatorio**"

#: src/container/security.md:183
msgid ""
"`untrusted` requires kernel-level isolation (i.e. a microVM, not a shared-"
"kernel container). When the active backend doesn't expose a microVM runtime "
"(`apple/container`'s VM mode, Lima, Firecracker), the engine returns "
"`BackendNotAvailable` rather than silently dropping the isolation guarantee."
" Use `PERRY_ALLOW_UNTRUSTED_SHARED_KERNEL=1` to opt out — **not recommended "
"for actually-untrusted code.**"
msgstr ""
"`untrusted` requiere aislamiento a nivel de kernel (es decir, una microVM, "
"no un contenedor de kernel compartido). Cuando el backend activo no expone "
"un runtime de microVM (el modo VM de `apple/container`, Lima, Firecracker), "
"el motor devuelve `BackendNotAvailable` en lugar de ignorar silenciosamente "
"la garantía de aislamiento. Use `PERRY_ALLOW_UNTRUSTED_SHARED_KERNEL=1` para"
" desactivar esta restricción — **no se recomienda para código realmente no "
"confiable.**"

#: src/container/security.md:190
msgid ""
"User-explicit per-flag overrides on top of a tier are honored: setting "
"`policy.tier = \"default\"` and `no_network: true` produces an isolated-"
"network default-tier node."
msgstr ""
"Las anulaciones explícitas por indicador sobre un nivel se respetan: "
"establecer `policy.tier = \"default\"` y `no_network: true` produce un nodo "
"de nivel predeterminado con red aislada."

