"(`/Applications`, `Program Files`). La ruta de instalación actual solo "
"maneja ubicaciones con permisos de escritura del usuario (`~/Applications`, "
"`~/.local/bin`, `%LOCALAPPDATA%`). UAC / `SMJobBless` es una preocupación "
"separada."

#: src/updater/overview.md:415
msgid ""
"**Delta updates** (bsdiff), **multi-channel** (stable / beta), **staged "
"rollouts**."
msgstr ""
"**Actualizaciones delta** (bsdiff), **multi-canal** (estable / beta), "
"**despliegues graduales**."

#: src/updater/overview.md:417
msgid ""
"**Notarization / code-signing** during install. Binaries are expected to "
"arrive already signed; the updater doesn't try to be a notarization tool."
msgstr ""
