#: src/system/audio_module.md:1
msgid "Audio (perry/audio)"
msgstr "Audio (perry/audio)"

#: src/system/audio_module.md:3
msgid ""
"The `perry/audio` module is Perry's **low-latency, game-engine-style audio "
"mixer**. Three concepts:"
msgstr ""
"El módulo `perry/audio` es el **mezclador de audio de baja latencia estilo "
"motor de juego** de Perry. Tres conceptos:"

#: src/system/audio_module.md:6
msgid ""
"**`Sound`** — a loaded asset. `loadSound(\"click.wav\")` returns one handle;"
" the PCM data lives in memory until you `unload()`."
msgstr ""
"**`Sound`** — un recurso cargado. `loadSound(\"click.wav\")` devuelve un "
"handle; los datos PCM permanecen en memoria hasta que llamas a `unload()`."

#: src/system/audio_module.md:8
msgid ""
"**`PlaybackId`** — one _live voice_. `play(sound)` returns a new PlaybackId "
"every time it's called, so the same sound can overlap with itself (think: "
"multiple gunshots, multiple footsteps)."
msgstr ""
"**`PlaybackId`** — una _voz activa_. `play(sound)` devuelve un nuevo "
"PlaybackId cada vez que se llama, por lo que el mismo sonido puede "
"superponerse consigo mismo (por ejemplo: múltiples disparos, múltiples "
"pasos)."

#: src/system/audio_module.md:11
msgid ""
"**`Bus`** — a mixer group. Sounds route through a Bus, Buses route through "
"their parent (default: master). One `setVolume(musicBus, 0.3)` scales every "
"voice on it."
msgstr ""
"**`Bus`** — un grupo mezclador. Los sonidos se enrutan a través de un Bus, y"
" los Buses se enrutan a través de su padre (por defecto: master). Un solo "
"`setVolume(musicBus, 0.3)` escala todas las voces en él."

#: src/system/audio_module.md:15
msgid ""
"Use `perry/audio` for SFX, music loops, voice prompts, and any UI feedback "
"where you want overlap or sub-20ms latency. For long-form streaming with a "
"seek bar, lock-screen controls, and Now Playing metadata, use "
"[`perry/media`](./media.md) instead."
msgstr ""
"Usa `perry/audio` para efectos de sonido, bucles de música, indicaciones de "
"voz y cualquier retroalimentación de UI donde necesites superposición o "
"latencia inferior a 20ms. Para transmisión de largo alcance con barra de "
"búsqueda, controles en pantalla de bloqueo y metadatos de Now Playing, usa "
"[`perry/media`](./media.md) en su lugar."

#: src/system/audio_module.md:22
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import {\n"
"  loadSound, play, stop, setVolume,\n"
"  createBus, setMasterVolume,\n"
"} from \"perry/audio\";\n"
"\n"
"// Optional: organise sounds into buses\n"
"const sfx   = createBus(\"sfx\");\n"
"const music = createBus(\"music\");\n"
"\n"
"// Load assets — decode happens in the background. The handle is\n"
"// returned immediately; play() before decode finishes just queues\n"
"// the playback.\n"
"const click = loadSound(\"assets/click.wav\", sfx);\n"
"const bgm   = loadSound(\"assets/bgm.mp3\",   music, /* stream */ true);\n"
"\n"
"// Fire-and-forget — overlap is automatic, each play() returns a new\n"
"// PlaybackId you can stop / fade / tune independently.\n"
"const a = play(click);\n"
"const b = play(click, 0.7, false, 0.95);  // slightly lower pitch\n"
"const bgmId = play(bgm, 1.0, true);        // looping\n"
"\n"
"// Mix\n"
"setVolume(music, 0.3);\n"
"setMasterVolume(0.8);\n"
"\n"
"// Stop\n"
"stop(a);          // one voice\n"
"stop(click);      // every live voice of this sound\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/system/audio_module.md:53
msgid "Game-engine patterns"
msgstr "Patrones de motor de juego"

#: src/system/audio_module.md:55
msgid "Pitch variation on repeated SFX"
msgstr "Variación de tono en efectos de sonido repetidos"

#: src/system/audio_module.md:57
msgid ""
"The single biggest \"doesn't feel robotic\" trick: randomise the rate (±5%) "
"on every play of high-frequency SFX (footsteps, gunshots, hits)."
msgstr ""
"El mayor truco para que «no suene robótico»: aleatoriza la tasa (±5%) en "
"cada reproducción de efectos de sonido de alta frecuencia (pasos, disparos, "
"golpes)."

#: src/system/audio_module.md:60
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const rate = 0.95 + Math.random() * 0.1;  // 0.95 – 1.05\n"
"play(footstep, 1.0, false, rate);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/system/audio_module.md:65
msgid "Crossfade music tracks"
msgstr "Fundido cruzado de pistas de música"

#: src/system/audio_module.md:67
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"const calmId = play(calm, 0.0, true);   // start silent\n"
"crossfade(intenseId, calmId, 2000);     // 2s linear crossfade\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/system/audio_module.md:72
msgid "Pause when backgrounded"
msgstr "Pausar al pasar a segundo plano"

#: src/system/audio_module.md:74
