"`NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription` in `Info.plist`. Backed by "
"`CLLocationManager`."
msgstr ""
"`NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription` en `Info.plist`. Respaldado por "
"`CLLocationManager`."

#: src/system/geolocation.md:64
msgid ""
"`<uses-permission "
"android:name=\"android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION\"/>` (or "
"`ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION`) in `AndroidManifest.xml`. Backed by "
