"**Extensiones que disparan el trigger:** `.ts`, `.tsx`, `.mts`, `.cts`, "
"`.json`, `.toml`"

#: src/cli/commands.md:126
msgid ""
"**Ignored directories (not watched, never retrigger):** `node_modules`, "
"`target`, `.git`, `dist`, `build`, `.perry-dev`, `.perry-cache`"
msgstr ""
"**Directorios ignorados (no observados, nunca disparan):** `node_modules`, "
