#: src/contributing/architecture.md:58
msgid ""
"Generational mark-sweep GC, per-thread arena split into nursery + old-gen. "
"Roots come from a precise shadow stack (emitted by codegen), a conservative "
"native-stack scan, and 9 registered runtime scanners. Two-bit aging tenures "
"objects after surviving 2 minor cycles; a write barrier maintains a "
"remembered set for old → young pointers."
msgstr ""
"GC de marca y barrido generacional, arena por hilo dividida en nursery + "
"old-gen. Las raíces provienen de un shadow stack preciso (emitido por el "
"codegen), un escaneo conservador de la pila nativa y 9 escáneres de runtime "
"registrados. El envejecimiento de dos bits promueve objetos a tenured tras "
"sobrevivir 2 ciclos menores; una barrera de escritura mantiene un conjunto "
"de recordados para punteros de old → young."

#: src/contributing/architecture.md:60
msgid ""
"See [Internals → Memory Model](../internals/memory-model.md) for the full "
"picture (NaN-boxing, heap layout, root discovery, generational behaviour, "
"env-var escape hatches)."
msgstr ""
"Consulta [Internals → Memory Model](../internals/memory-model.md) para el "
"panorama completo (NaN-boxing, disposición del heap, descubrimiento de "
"raíces, comportamiento generacional, variables de entorno de escape)."

#: src/contributing/architecture.md:62
msgid "Handle-Based UI"
msgstr "UI basada en handles"

#: src/contributing/architecture.md:64
msgid ""
"UI widgets are represented as small integer handles NaN-boxed with "
"`POINTER_TAG`. Each handle maps to a native platform widget (NSButton, "
"UILabel, GtkButton, etc.). Two dispatch tables route method calls and "
"property accesses to the correct FFI function."
msgstr ""
"Los widgets de UI se representan como handles de entero pequeño NaN-boxed "
"con `POINTER_TAG`. Cada handle se asigna a un widget de plataforma nativa "
"(NSButton, UILabel, GtkButton, etc.). Dos tablas de despacho enrutan las "
"llamadas a métodos y los accesos a propiedades a la función FFI correcta."

